name: Rowena Screenplay Concept
description: Circa 2016; shortly after character creation and concepts for the world that is "Rowena", I began working on a draft for a screenplay. My friends Peighton and Courtney agreed to be characters and actresses in the screenplay as the characters Kaia and Nia. This particular script introduces Rowena via a portal opening in the state of New Jersey, where Nia and Kaia reside.
